metadata.name: Angry Sheep - Honorary Members #1
metadata.description: Angry Sheep - Honorary Members is a special collection of 50 Angry Sheep NFTs — unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain which are given in recognition of helping, supporting and raising awareness of the Angry Sheep Club. Your Angry Sheep - Honorary Members is more than just a collector’s item: it offers member-only benefits that you enjoy by becoming a Holder member of Angry Sheep Club. Angry Sheep Club is a private membership club that functions according to its own Bylaws. Angry Sheep Club has and maintains separate and equal station status among all other entities. We have created a place where members can meet, discuss and access a variety of opportunities for personal and professional growth on Discord. Visit https://discord.gg/angrysheepclub to join the Club.
